# 3. SSL Certificate

Generate certificate.

```bash
sudo certbot --nginx \
-d mail.blessed.co.zw
```

Certificates are stored in

```
/etc/letsencrypt/live/mail.blessed.co.zw/
```

Verify

```bash
sudo certbot certificates
```

