# 4. Postfix Configuration

Main configuration

```
/etc/postfix/main.cf
```

## Important Settings

```ini
compatibility_level = 3.9

myhostname = mail.blessed.co.zw

myorigin = /etc/mailname

inet_interfaces = all

inet_protocols = all

mydestination = localhost

relayhost = [smtp-relay.brevo.com]:587

smtp_sasl_auth_enable = yes

smtp_sasl_password_maps = static:BREVO_USERNAME:BREVO_SMTP_KEY

smtp_sasl_security_options = noanonymous

smtp_tls_CAfile = /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

smtp_tls_security_level = encrypt

smtpd_tls_cert_file = /etc/letsencrypt/live/mail.blessed.co.zw/fullchain.pem

smtpd_tls_key_file = /etc/letsencrypt/live/mail.blessed.co.zw/privkey.pem

smtpd_tls_security_level = may
```

Restart

```bash
sudo systemctl restart postfix
```

Verify

```bash
sudo postfix check
```

