# 6. Dovecot Configuration

Main configuration.

```
/etc/dovecot/
```

Verify configuration.

```bash
sudo doveconf -n
```

Required configuration.

```conf
protocols = imap lmtp

ssl = required

mail_driver = maildir

mail_path = ~/Maildir

passdb pam {
}

userdb passwd {
}
```

SSL

```conf
ssl_server {

    cert_file = /etc/letsencrypt/live/mail.blessed.co.zw/fullchain.pem

    key_file = /etc/letsencrypt/live/mail.blessed.co.zw/privkey.pem

}
```

Restart

```bash
sudo systemctl restart dovecot
```

