# 14. Common Mistakes

## Wrong hostname

Use

```
mail.blessed.co.zw
```

NOT

```
www.blessed.co.zw
```

---

## Cloudflare Proxy

Mail records must never be proxied.

---

## Snakeoil Certificates

Never use

```
ssl-cert-snakeoil.pem
```

Use Let's Encrypt.

---

## Reverse DNS

PTR must resolve to

```
mail.blessed.co.zw
```
Make sure your machine hostname is set to your domain (base/mail.base as long as IP points to server static IP)

---

## Brevo

Sender addresses must belong to your authenticated domain.

---

## Username Format

Use

```
info@blessed.co.zw
```

NOT Linux usernames when configuring end-user mail clients.

Dovecot will convert the email address to the Linux username internally.

---

## Authentication Testing

Always verify with

```bash
sudo doveadm auth test info@blessed.co.zw
```

before testing in Outlook or mobile mail clients.

